- Uh, no, just no!

1:20:38.668 --> 1:20:41.306
Not even close!

1:20:41.341 --> 1:20:42.868
- What, like that?

1:20:42.903 --> 1:20:44.980
- Oh!

1:20:45.015 --> 1:20:46.707
- No!
- Hit it.

1:20:53.716 --> 1:20:56.288
- One second!
One second!

