1:36:07.134 --> 1:36:09.794
YOLI V.O.: I look at that
photograph and wonder,

1:36:09.829 --> 1:36:13.534
were the lines already drawn
and we just didn't know it?

1:36:13.569 --> 1:36:16.702
♪

1:36:16.737 --> 1:36:19.276
