1:36:19.311 --> 1:36:22.477
Elf's favourite poem
was "On Friendship"

1:36:22.512 --> 1:36:25.447
by Samuel Coleridge.

1:36:25.482 --> 1:36:30.287
"I too a sister had,
an only sister.

1:36:30.322 --> 1:36:34.896
"She loved me dearly
and I doted on her.

1:36:34.931 --> 1:36:38.229
"To her I poured forth
all my puny sorrows."

1:36:38.264 --> 1:36:42.002
♪

1:36:42.037 --> 1:36:45.599
- Did you actually think I'd
get that inscribed on my back?

1:36:49.803 --> 1:36:53.640
- For a minute there
I was worried, so yes, I did.

1:36:53.675 --> 1:36:56.049
Wouldn't be entirely
out of character.

1:36:56.084 --> 1:36:58.315
- Can you imagine trying
to explain that to a guy

1:36:58.350 --> 1:37:00.988
you're about to have sex with?

1:37:05.489 --> 1:37:07.324
- Might be
a bit of a mood-killer.

1:37:07.359 --> 1:37:09.524
- I'd never get laid again.

1:37:09.559 --> 1:37:11.691
- Don't sell yourself short.
You're a catch.

1:37:11.726 --> 1:37:14.067
- Hmm, that's true.

1:37:14.102 --> 1:37:17.268
I do come with drawbacks
that are not readily evident.

1:37:22.143 --> 1:37:24.572
- Do you remember when
we watched that solar eclipse?

1:37:29.018 --> 1:37:32.382
- It was so cold.

1:37:32.417 --> 1:37:35.990
- We wore welding helmets,
didn't we?

1:37:36.025 --> 1:37:37.926
- Where did you get them?

1:37:37.961 --> 1:37:39.752
- I forget.

1:37:39.787 --> 1:37:42.931
Some guy I knew.

1:37:42.966 --> 1:37:45.890
- It was amazing,
wasn't it?

1:37:45.925 --> 1:37:47.529
- Yes.

1:37:53.042 --> 1:37:55.438
The path of totality.

1:37:55.473 --> 1:37:58.078
- Is that what it's called?

1:37:58.113 --> 1:38:00.905
- Yeah.

1:38:00.940 --> 1:38:05.844
Don't you remember
what Dad said?

1:38:05.879 --> 1:38:10.090
The path of totality passed
over us in the early afternoon.

1:38:16.923 --> 1:38:19.264
- The next one's
not supposed to be

1:38:19.299 --> 1:38:21.794
for 1,500 years
or something like that.

1:38:23.765 --> 1:38:26.106
- Then I guess I'll miss it.

1:38:26.141 --> 1:38:29.571
- Me too, I suppose.

1:38:29.606 --> 1:38:30.902
- Who knows?

1:38:34.941 --> 1:38:36.776
Who knows?

1:38:49.263 --> 1:38:50.966
What's your book about?

1:39:07.908 --> 1:39:09.248
- Us.

1:39:17.060 --> 1:39:18.719
It's about us.

